text: Linnethia Monique "NeNe" Leakes (; n√©e Johnson; born on December 13, 1967) is an American television personality, actress, presenter, author, and fashion designer. She is best known for having appeared on the reality television series The Real Housewives of Atlanta as an original cast member.
